{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1271","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1271/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1271/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/1271/events","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/1271","id":10224459,"number":1271,"title":"error while installing 3rdparty apps","user":{"login":"jbazinga","id":2959334,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8cc91e34c1869ae29d784b4592b01e6c?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f3b38a3ea639fcb3e1137d00f8de72e65.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8cc91e34c1869ae29d784b4592b01e6c","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga","html_url":"https://github.com/jbazinga","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jbazinga/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","assignee":null,"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2013-01-23t08:38:11z","updated_at":"2013-03-01t11:36:17z","closed_at":"2013-03-01t11:36:17z","pull_request":{"html_url":null,"diff_url":null,"patch_url":null},"body":"hello\r\n\r\ni got an error, when i try to install the 3rdparty apps.\r\n\r\nwhen i browse the source code, i found the bug, and fixed it.\r\nsteps of the error:\r\nwhen i would like to install the app in the settings/apps page the system download the compressed file to the /tmp folder without any extension. after that the system would like to detect the mime type, but it can not do that, because the downloaded file in /tmp folder does not got any extension...\r\n\r\nso i fixed the lib/installer.php file installapp method like this:\r\n\r\nafter line 65 (  if($data['source']=='http') { )  detect the remote file's extension like this:\r\n$extension = substr($data['href'], strrpos($data['href'], '.'));\r\nif ( extension === \".gz\" ) $extension = \".tar.gz\";\r\n\r\nand then \r\nadd this extension to tmpfile generator like this:\r\n\r\n$path=oc_helper::tmpfile($extension);\r\n\r\nand all works fine\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"jancborchardt","id":925062,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f84ec51f9ceed468217d4e13abf78da9c.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt","html_url":"https://github.com/jancborchardt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}